{"tid":524787,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳帆掌機電署期間 潘公司獲數千萬元工程","createTime":"2018-01-10T03:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T04:01:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ac51682e852bccd8d13ec2eeb3efaa7128c7653a","tid":524787,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T03:19:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180110/20270082\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180110%2F20270082&d=wbybNbZG5TiC%2FlbXGPiTWBFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=a9602f72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180110%2F20270082&h=c8a67633\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180110/20270082</a><br />\n<br />\n陳帆掌機電署期間<br />\n潘公司獲數千萬元工程<br />\n<br />\n頭條   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】運房局長陳帆曾於2016年12月為鄭若驊及潘樂陶證婚，陳更是潘的證婚人，反映二人私交甚篤。翻查紀錄，潘所創立的安樂工程集團曾多次取得機電署工程標書，包括機電工程署九龍灣總部內的空調系統、小濠灣污水處理廠設置除臭設備裝置等，部份合約金額達數千萬元，有工程界擔心二人若有生意往來，或涉利益衝突。<br />\n<br />\n運房局發言人日前證實局長陳帆是潘樂陶與鄭若驊的婚禮證婚人，又指陳曾到訪潘的大屋，而期間陳出任機電工程署署長。翻查資料，陳2001年晉升為總電子工程師，至2005年任政府機電工程師，至2011年出任機電署署長。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180110/large/a0206a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180110%2Flarge%2Fa0206a.gif&h=be384b48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳帆（左圖）與潘樂陶（右圖）私交甚篤，工程界質疑二人或涉利益衝突。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n份屬好友　外界憂私相授受<br />\n<br />\n潘所創立的安樂工程集團，公司網頁顯示，在2001至2011年間，安樂曾取得不少機電署工程合約，包括2003年完工的機電署及資訊科技署設於荃灣的數據中心內，採購及安裝不間斷電源工程；2006年完工的機電署九龍灣總部內，設計、採購及安裝機房空調系統等。機電署網頁亦顯示，安樂曾於2010年承接九龍灣綜合回收中心的試驗堆肥設施改善、營運及保養服務，估計標價為2,368萬元；2014年亦承接整個九龍區的市政場地內消防裝置維修及保養，標價1,857萬元。<br />\n有資深工程師指，陳在機電署任內多年，有機會接觸涉及判標工作，若涉較重要的標書亦有機會由署長或高層拍板，他認為雖二人為朋友而非屬親屬關係，「但會唔會有生意來往呢？係咪申報咗會比較好？否則畀人有私相授受感覺」。本報曾向運房局及機電署查詢，暫未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鍾雅宜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180110/large/a0206b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180110%2Flarge%2Fa0206b.gif&h=30b74cab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n\t倘主理僭建　業主或需負刑責<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t泛民提緊急質詢　梁君彥拒絕<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t鄭若驊與夫孖屋9處僭建　屋宇署調查揭起多1,500呎林鄭：她無隱瞞，仍是非常理想司長<br />\n頭條 5小時前"},{"pid":"24461194b75229fec153ab0cbe1adb172a2fd21d","tid":524787,"uid":35219,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T03:24:15.000Z","msg":"繼續爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4fbfc3d948b024e25f1e82547d72a6a81adf83","tid":524787,"uid":164167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T03:25:00.000Z","msg":"香港<br />\n勝在有貪污徇私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1104c333fb1556a8e55666e568c47c28430561","tid":524787,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T03:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n譚X芝:你老味查得太盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172daba6ef74ac0c465a85fac80a372a6f756a14","tid":524787,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T03:26:34.000Z","msg":"等睇傻鳩話<br />\n其他地方都有<br />\n香港已經好少<img src=\"